* Madhav Abhyankar as Swamy Sudarshan Maharaj
* Pournima Manohar as Omkar's Mother
* Vinayak Bhave as Manohar Swamy<ref>{{cite web|title=Surajya Marathi Movie |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jOQNb_oJOUc|accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref>

